=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_LinCongC_ex3 ===

DESCRIPTION: A bright gritty sound, with complex oscillator character around 53 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: gritty
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 52.9732
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.1619
  harmonic_regularity: 0.1709
  pitch_clarity: 17.3598
  inharmonicity: 0.0455
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -30.4551
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

